data.description: Spacious 5 bedroom home on a corner lot! This home  has  had some upgrades in the last couple years including newer windows and a remodeled Bathroom. Garage has an extra room that can be used as a Man Cave, storage, or guest room.  There are  3 Bedrooms downstairs and 2 upstairs. One bedroom downstairs is being used as a storage. Utility room has a half bath in it.
